On the other hand, amino acid metabolites were barely detectable within CD133+ cells compared with those in other fractions.
('amino acid metabolites', 'were detectable within', 'CD133')

CE-TOF-MS analyses revealed that 28 metabolites were upregulated while 53 metabolites were downregulated in CD133-positive cells ().
('metabolites', 'were downregulated in', 'cells')

These metabolome results reinforced the exclusiveness of the phenotype observed within the CD133+ cell population derived from the Colo205 cell line.
('results', 'reinforced', 'exclusiveness of phenotype observed within CD133 population derived from Colo205 cell line')

