('cultures', 'lead to', 'restructuring of metabolome')

As phenotypic differences had been highlighted among cultured Colo205 cells, we performed CE-TOF-MS on these cells.
('differences', 'had been highlighted among', 'Colo205 cells')

The results indicated that serum-free culture (for three to five weeks) led to overall increases in the metabolome related to glycogenosis, glycolysis, the citrate cycle, amino acid synthesis and nucleotide metabolism pathways.
('culture', 'led to', 'increases in metabolome')

