To assess the sorting process of the Colo205 cell line, selected cells were stained by both relevant monoclonal antibodies: PE-conjugated AC133/2-PE antibody (130-090-853, 1/200; Miltenyi Biotec) and PE-conjugated CD44-PE antibody (130-095-180, 1/200; Miltenyi Biotec), or with similarly conjugated isotype-matched antibodies, for 30 minutes at 4°C.
