Metabolite standards, instrumentation and CE-TOF-MS conditions.

Instrumentation and CE-TOF-MS conditions followed the Human Metabolome Technologies guidelines (HMT Inc.).
('Instrumentation conditions', 'followed', 'Metabolome Technologies guidelines')

CE-TOF-MS experiments were performed on an Agilent capillary electrophoresis system coupled to an Agilent 6224 CE/TOF-MS analyzer (Agilent Technologies).
